<H3> <TI>   Returns to Work </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Returns to Work </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MB0205124894 Johannesburg SAPA in English 1206 GMT 2 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> MB0205124894 </F>
