<H3> <TI>   Air Force To Retain Name; SADF To Change </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Air Force To Retain Name; SADF To Change </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MB2904191594 Johannesburg SAPA in English 1843 GMT 29 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> MB2904191594 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg SAPA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pretoria April 29 SAPA -- The SA Air Force [SAAF] 
would retain its title even though the SA Defence Force would 
change its name to the SA National Defence Force, it was 
announced on Friday [29 April]. 
  SAAF headquarters said in a statement that when referred to 
as part of the defence community, the term SA National Defence 
Force would encompass the Army, Navy, Medical Services and the 
Air Force. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

