color, and voted therefore for the African National Congress. 
  [Newton] In anticipation of the expected celebrations, Mr. 
Lekota appealed to supporters not to misbehave. 
  [Lekota] I want to urge our members and supporters, and 
well- 
wishers to behave with utmost discipline and comeliness. [end 
recording] 

