<F P=105>  Portuguese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Mozambican nationals living abroad do not yet have 
the green light to vote in the first general and multiparty 
elections in Mozambique scheduled for October. A source from 
the National Elections Commission revealed yesterday that voting 
will not take place abroad unless a consensus that necessary 
material conditions and control and supervision mechanisms for 
the voting process have been created. 

