<F P=103> MB0205223094 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
BFN 

    [Editorial Report] Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network in 
English on 2 May at 1830 GMT reports that projections show the 
following seat distribution in the National Assembly: 
  African National Congress: 251 seats 
  National Party: 95 seats 
  Inkatha Freedom Party: 25 seats 
  Freedom Front: 12 seats 
  Democratic Party: 8 seats 
  Pan Africanist Congress: 5 seats 

