  [Text] Public officers are now free to contest the election 
into the national constitutional conference. The chairman of 
the conference election committee, Mr. Bernard Mba, disclosed 
this today in Abuja at a news conference. Mr. Mba said the 
officers will be given leave of absence by their employers to 
