delegates are to be elected at the ward level, (?and) the 
constituent district level will elect a delegate for the 
conference. [sentence as heard] The chairman stated that all 
Nigerians who have attained the age of 18 are eligible to vote. 
Mr. Mba disclosed that a committee will be constituted as part 
of local government [word indistinct] to administer the 
elections. He also called on Nigerians to ensure the success of 
the exercise. 

