this morning. Government and UNITA forces were fighting in the 
area of Cuchi, some 100 km from Menongue, an area which was 
reoccupied by the Angolan Armed Forces, FAA, a few days ago. 
Commander Silva reported that the FALA forces were assembling 
sophisticated war materiel to intensify the fighting. [passage 
omitted] 

